  "title": "Vehicle Attendant",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for organized and motivated vehicle attendants to join our team. The vehicle attendants will work together with the drivers as a team to plan delivery routing, check and load the truck, and unloading at customer’s premise.</p><p><br /></p><p>Duties and Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Loading and unloading of cargoes.</li><li>Assisting drivers to find delivery locations.</li><li>Effectively communicating with clients and customers to resolve complaints.</li><li>Reporting all delivery-related problems to senior staff.</li><li>Obtaining customers’ signatures as an acknowledgment of having received the delivered products.</li><li>Ensuring that all safety policies and procedures are adhered to.</li></ul>",
